subject: Hello,
body:
Hello,
This transaction will be legally conducted. I would like to present to you a life changing opportunity that will benefit both of us greatly. If you are interested, reply and I will provide details.
Thanks,
Michael.

subject: Re:  Hello,
body:
Hello Michael,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm always interested in hearing about life-changing opportunities. Could you please provide me with more details about what you have in mind? I'd love to learn more.

Best wishes,
Jaime
